~+~+duck-the-virus+~+~


~+~+~+~+~+~+
Requirements
~+~+~+~+~+~+

python3.6 -m pip install -r requirements.txt

~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~
How to play 
~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~

* Keys

* [up arrow] - move up

* [down-arrow]  - move down

* [left-arrow]  - move left

* [right-arrow] - move right

* [space-key] - activate shield

* [esc-key] - quit

* [pause-key] - pause for 5 seconds.

~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~+~

